<section class="paranoia-theme-lab">
  <div>
    <h2>Extracted palette</h2>
    <p>The cream and blue form the reading surface. Rust, olive, mustard, and brown supply the bureaucratic cheer, warnings, stamps, rules, and ornamental geometry.</p>
    <div class="paranoia-palette" aria-label="Paranoia color palette">
      <div class="paranoia-swatch paranoia-swatch--brown">#774C1D</div>
      <div class="paranoia-swatch paranoia-swatch--cream">#FFF9F0</div>
      <div class="paranoia-swatch paranoia-swatch--rust">#903C1D</div>
      <div class="paranoia-swatch paranoia-swatch--blue">#325B6D</div>
      <div class="paranoia-swatch paranoia-swatch--green">#4E5B27</div>
      <div class="paranoia-swatch paranoia-swatch--gold">#EDAF54</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Three possible directions</h2>
    <div class="paranoia-concepts">
      <article class="paranoia-concept paranoia-concept--civic">
        <p class="paranoia-concept__kicker">Concept A · Futura + Lato</p>
        <h3>Civic Modern</h3>
        <p>Clean government-brochure geometry with cheerful color blocks and firm typographic hierarchy.</p>
        <div class="paranoia-concept__memo">
          <strong>MANDATORY WELLNESS NOTICE</strong><br>
          Happiness is efficient. Efficiency is loyalty.
        </div>
        <span class="paranoia-concept__status">Clearance approved</span>
      </article>

      <article class="paranoia-concept paranoia-concept--friendly">
        <p class="paranoia-concept__kicker">Concept B · Seraphine Round</p>
        <h3>Friendly Computer</h3>
        <p>Softer, rounder, and more playfully sinister—like a children’s educational film with terrible consequences.</p>
        <div class="paranoia-concept__memo">
          <strong>SMILE, CITIZEN!</strong><br>
          Your cooperation has already been recorded.
        </div>
        <span class="paranoia-concept__status">Fun is mandatory</span>
      </article>

      <article class="paranoia-concept paranoia-concept--directive">
        <p class="paranoia-concept__kicker">Concept C · Quaint Gothic + Georgia</p>
        <h3>Executive Directive</h3>
        <p>A slightly more literary retro treatment: corporate annual report meets classified civil-defense handbook.</p>
        <div class="paranoia-concept__memo">
          <strong>DIRECTIVE 774-C</strong><br>
          Unauthorized uncertainty is punishable by reassignment.
        </div>
        <span class="paranoia-concept__status">Eyes only</span>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="callout">
    <strong>My recommendation:</strong> use Civic Modern as the default system theme, borrow Friendly Computer’s rounded shapes for surveys and playful notices, and reserve Executive Directive for classified handouts or long-form lore.
  </div>
</section>
